headline: Tradr Set to Debut ETFs Targeting Bloom Energy, Celestica, Nano Nuclear and Synopsys
summary: Tradr ETFs, a provider of ETFs designed for sophisticated investors and professional traders, announced that it expects to launch four new single stock leveraged ETFs on Thursday, November 13. The funds will be listed on Cboe and all four represent first-to-market strategies. Each ETF aims to deliver twice (200%) the daily performance of its specific underlying stock.

headline: Is Synopsys (SNPS) a Buy as Wall Street Analysts Look Optimistic?
summary: The average brokerage recommendation (ABR) for Synopsys (SNPS) is equivalent to a Buy. The overly optimistic recommendations of Wall Street analysts make the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric questionable. So, is it worth buying the stock?
